 104:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\drivers/peripheral/tcpwm/cy_tcpwm.h **** * 
 105:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\drivers/peripheral/tcpwm/cy_tcpwm.h **** * The Quadrature Decoder has the following features:
 106:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\drivers/peripheral/tcpwm/cy_tcpwm.h **** * * 16- or 32-bit Counter
 107:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\drivers/peripheral/tcpwm/cy_tcpwm.h **** * * Counter Resolution of x1, x2, and x4 the frequency of the phiA (Count) and 
