 109:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\drivers/peripheral/tcpwm/cy_tcpwm.h **** * * Index Input to determine absolute position
 110:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\drivers/peripheral/tcpwm/cy_tcpwm.h **** * * A positive edge on phiA increments the counter when phiB is 0 and decrements
